title: Vital Tarashchyk
text:
Vital Tarashchyk (; ; born 18 May 1980) is a retired <a href="Belarus">Belarus</a>ian professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a>er. His latest club was <a href="FC%20Lida">Lida</a> in 2013. In 2016, he worked as <a href="FC%20Lida">FC Lida</a> head coach.
Honours.
MTZ-RIPO Minsk
Naftan Novopolotsk
